If you listen to the tape
you can form your own opinion.

1502
01:19:28,308 --> 01:19:31,979
And so when I wrote my book
I kept out a lot of things,

1503
01:19:32,146 --> 01:19:33,940
stuff that I would never
write about

1504
01:19:34,107 --> 01:19:36,151
cause, remember,
when the book was coming out

1505
01:19:36,318 --> 01:19:38,362
I was still protecting his image.

1506
01:19:38,529 --> 01:19:41,074
Evel's attorney,
he checked everything.

1507
01:19:41,241 --> 01:19:42,993
Told me
that it had Evel's approval

1508
01:19:43,160 --> 01:19:44,495
in writing.

1509
01:19:44,662 --> 01:19:46,622
Then the book was published.

1510
01:19:47,290 --> 01:19:49,292
I was at Evel's compound one day.

1511
01:19:49,459 --> 01:19:51,212
He throws me this book.

1512
