1526
01:20:33,765 --> 01:20:35,893
I didn't see anything in it bad.
Nothing.

1527
01:20:36,059 --> 01:20:40,064
It was very factual.
Very, very, very factual.

1528
01:20:40,231 --> 01:20:45,446
I think that Shelly, who wrote it,
was accurate.

1529
01:20:45,613 --> 01:20:48,033
And...

1530
01:20:48,200 --> 01:20:50,828
it made him really mad.

1531
01:20:52,789 --> 01:20:55,208
I was on the 20th Century Fox lot.

1532
01:20:55,375 --> 01:20:56,877
All of a sudden
I saw Evel

1533
01:20:57,044 --> 01:20:59,506
with a big smile
coming at me loping along.

1534
01:21:00,966 --> 01:21:03,469
I was actually glad to see him.
The book was out.

1535
01:21:03,636 --> 01:21:06,723
I was like maybe I can even talk him
into doing some promotion with me.

1536
01:21:06,890 --> 01:21:08,267
I said "Hey, Evel."

1537
01:21:08,433 --> 01:21:12,105
And all of a sudden, my hands...
they were held behind my back.

1538
01:21:12,272 --> 01:21:14,024
They tell me it was two men.

1539
01:21:14,191 --> 01:21:15,818
It may have been one.
It may have been two.

1540
01:21:15,985 --> 01:21:18,613
And he...
He came at me

1541
01:21:18,780 --> 01:21:22,117
with a bat...
an aluminium baseball bat.

1542
01:21:22,284 --> 01:21:25,371
He said "I'm gonna kill you,
you son of a bitch."

1543
01:21:25,538 --> 01:21:28,333
I did everything I could
to defend myself.

1544
01:21:28,500 --> 01:21:30,002
I remember putting my hand up

1545
01:21:30,169 --> 01:21:32,130
and said "What are you doing?
What are you doing?"

1546
01:21:32,297 --> 01:21:33,590
I was fighting for my life.

1547
01:21:33,757 --> 01:21:36,594
He was whaling on me
and then I passed out.

