01:21:46,523 --> 01:21:47,858
in the baseball bat attack

1552
01:21:48,025 --> 01:21:50,695
on television executive
Sheldon Saltman.

1553
01:21:50,862 --> 01:21:52,614
Knievel could
have gotten away with it.

1554
