or sometimes a tool helped.

1567
01:22:29,327 --> 01:22:31,162
Not with a baseball bat.

1568
01:22:32,038 --> 01:22:33,874
That's not Butte.

1569
01:22:34,041 --> 01:22:37,503
I never knew of anybody in Butte
that did that.

1570
