I would have killed
that lousy little bastard.

1574
01:22:47,975 --> 01:22:51,271
I broke his arms with a baseball bat,
which is what I think he deserved.

1575
01:22:51,438 --> 01:22:52,647
I'll guarantee you one thing,

1576
01:22:53,315 --> 01:22:55,151
he doesn't write
anything else about me.

1577
