AUDIENCE LAUGH
But I'm...

1578
01:22:57,821 --> 01:23:01,033
I think I was a sophomore
in high school at the time.

1579
01:23:01,200 --> 01:23:03,703
I was not proud of my dad
for doing that...

1580
01:23:03,870 --> 01:23:05,247
at all.

1581
01:23:05,413 --> 01:23:08,334
Stuntman Evel Knievel
got a jail sentence yesterday

1582
01:23:08,501 --> 01:23:11,254
for beating his former press agent
with a baseball bat.

1583
01:23:11,421 --> 01:23:13,882
NEWS: The judge told
the 39-year-old motorcycle daredevil

