So he's in jail
but he's on work release.

1595
01:23:46,256 --> 01:23:48,009
So he's only in there at night.

1596
01:23:48,175 --> 01:23:51,972
He would have his chauffeur
pick him up every morning

1597
01:23:52,139 --> 01:23:54,100
and take him to the bar.

1598
01:23:54,266 --> 01:23:56,185
NEWS: Knievel believes
in sharing the wealth.

