Putting him in jail,
he got more press...

1602
01:24:07,783 --> 01:24:09,160
than anything else.

1603
01:24:09,327 --> 01:24:11,830
There was no end to the shenanigans
that guy would pull.

1604
01:24:11,997 --> 01:24:13,332
NEWS: The inmates were amazed.

1605
01:24:13,499 --> 01:24:16,836
But the authorities
were not so enthusiastic.

1606
01:24:17,003 --> 01:24:18,338
Well, the judge got pissed.

1607
