He revoked Evel's
work-release privileges.

1608
01:24:22,343 --> 01:24:24,054
I was pissed off at him.

1609
01:24:24,221 --> 01:24:25,931
He started believing the hype

1610
01:24:26,098 --> 01:24:27,725
that he was totally impervious,

1611
01:24:27,892 --> 01:24:29,769
