01:25:24,963 --> 01:25:27,884
But it has set him back financially.

1630
01:25:28,051 --> 01:25:32,473
I hated to see him lose
everything he worked for...

1631
01:25:32,640 --> 01:25:34,350
in ten minutes.

1632
01:25:34,893 --> 01:25:38,522
When it was falling apart
