The bank came and got it.
The IRS sold it.

1639
01:25:56,294 --> 01:25:58,380
We loaded up all the furniture,

1640
01:25:58,547 --> 01:26:01,676
everything of any value,
from the saddles to guns...

1641
01:26:01,843 --> 01:26:04,430
We would just bring so much
out at a time.

1642
01:26:04,596 --> 01:26:06,682
We'd have a garage sale.

1643
01:26:06,849 --> 01:26:10,229
The arc of the skycycle is
like what happened to his career.

1644
01:26:10,395 --> 01:26:11,939
He was at the pinnacle.

1645
01:26:12,106 --> 01:26:14,567
Then he destroyed
his whole life.

1646
01:26:15,902 --> 01:26:18,614
I just dropped out of site
and played golf.

1647
