He was kinda just getting by...

1651
01:26:29,795 --> 01:26:30,838
hustling golf...

1652
01:26:31,005 --> 01:26:33,216
he might make a couple hundred here,
a couple hundred there.

1653
01:26:33,383 --> 01:26:35,385
He lived day to day at that time.

1654
01:26:35,969 --> 01:26:39,640
He didn't keep the fact that
he was married a secret or anything.

1655
01:26:39,807 --> 01:26:43,395
In two weeks, I packed up
what I wanted to take with me

1656
01:26:43,562 --> 01:26:45,565
and we went on the road.

1657
01:26:46,983 --> 01:26:49,653
I just let it go at that.

1658
01:26:49,820 --> 01:26:51,363
The heck with it, you know.

1659
